  <p>TO INCLUDE AN <b>ALERT</b> COMPONENT:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>
      Code a <pre>div</pre> element. Add an <pre>.alert</pre> class to the div to define it as Kickstart Alert Component.
    </li>
    <li>
      Add the one or more Kickstart classes, separated by spaces, to the element using the class attribute.
    </li>
    <li>
      Add a
      <pre>data-dismiss=".alert"</pre>
      attribute and quoted class value for the closing the alert.
      <iframe width="100%" height="200" src="//jsfiddle.net/dgabhawala/h8ym2ftj/1/embedded/html/" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" allowpaymentrequest frameborder="0"></iframe>
    </li>
  </ol>
